These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, chinese, polish, mexican
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, marigold, begonia, daffodil
1. the chinese is between the argentine and the person who growsmarigold##2
2. the chinese is on the left or right of the person who growszinnia##3
3. the chinese is somewhere between the mexican and the argentine##7
4. the person who growsmarigold is in an even position##4
5. the mexican is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
6. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere to the left of the person who growszinnia##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Nationality   | polish | mexican       | chinese | argentine        |
| Flower      | begonia  | marigold | daffodil        | zinnia |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, colombian, argentine, brazilian
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, techno, d&b, metal
1. the fan metal is somewhere between the fan d&b and the argentine##7
2. the brazilian is somewhere to the left of the mexican##5
3. the brazilian is somewhere to the right of the fan metal##5
4. the colombian is on the left of the brazilian##1
5. the fan metal is between the fan d&b and the fan techno##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Nationality     | argentine | colombian       | brazilian         | mexican     |
| Music-Genre   | techno   | metal | d&b | dubstep |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, september, december, april
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, 7up, fanta, sprite
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking sprite is somewhere between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking milk##7
3. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
4. the person drinking milk is somewhere between the person drinking sprite and the person who's birthday is in september##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Birthday   | september | april | december | august  |
| Beverage   | fanta | milk  | sprite   | 7up |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, roller, bus, bike
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, spy, adventure, sports
1. the person watching sports movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere between the person watching spy movies and the person driving the bike##7
3. the person driving the bus is the person watching sports movies##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
5. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Transport   | roller | motorbike | bike       | bus |
| Movie-Genre   | spy      | mystery   | adventure | sports  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, teacher, writer, chef
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, snowmobile, skateboard, subway
1. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the teacher##3
2. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##5
3. the electrician is on the right of the writer##1
4. the person driving the subway is somewhere between the teacher and the electrician##7
5. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
6. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5
7. the teacher is on the far left or far right##3
8. the electrician is on the left or right of the writer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Job         | writer | electrician   | chef | teacher |
| Transport   | tram      | snowmobile | subway      | skateboard |

