.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, architect, chef, writer
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, subway, jet-ski, bike
1. the chef is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is the writer##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the right of the teacher##1
4. the teacher is on the left of the chef##1
5. the architect is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
6. the person driving the bike is somewhere between the person driving the train and the person driving the subway##7
7. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the right of the chef##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Job      | architect | teacher      | chef | writer     |
| Transport   | train    | bike | subway   | jet-ski |

