.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, emerald, blood-red, ivory
City: london, san-francisco, nizza, edinburgh
1. the person traveling to london is on the far left##1
2. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
3. the person who likes ivory is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is somewhere between the person who likes pink and the person who likes blood-red##7
5. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere to the left of the person who likes blood-red##5
6. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the person traveling to nizza##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Color          | ivory    | pink   | emerald | blood-red  |
| City   | london | nizza | edinburgh    | san-francisco |

