.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, daffodil, daisy, amaryllis
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, pop, r&b, jazz
1. the person who growsdaffodil is not the fan jazz##6
2. the fan r&b is on the left or right of the fan jazz##3
3. the person who growsamaryllis is the fan r&b##1
4. the person who growsdaisy is somewhere between the person who growsamaryllis and the person who growsbegonia##7
5. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
6. the fan jazz is on the right of the fan r&b##1
7. the fan jazz is on the left of the fan soul##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Flower   | amaryllis | daisy | daffodil | begonia |
| Music-Genre           | r&b   | jazz    | soul       | pop  |

