.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-9::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, romance, superhero, spy
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, scooter, taxi, ship
1. the person watching family movies is not the person driving the helicopter##6
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3
4. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
5. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere between the person driving the ship and the person watching romance movies##7
6. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
| Movie-Genre           | spy | family | superhero | romance |
| Transport   | ship         | taxi      | helicopter | scooter            |

