.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-10::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, banana, artichoke, onion
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, traveling, gardening, video-games
1. the person eating onion is somewhere between the person eating cauliflower and the person who's hobby is video-games##7
2. the person eating banana is not the person who's hobby is gardening##6
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is not the person eating artichoke##6
4. the person eating artichoke is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##5
5. the person eating cauliflower is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
6. the person eating onion is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Food   | cauliflower | onion | banana | artichoke |
| Hobby           | board-games    | traveling   | video-games  | gardening      |

