.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, puzzles, traveling, collecting
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, mirinda, lemonade, 7up
1. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##5
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person drinking mirinda##2
6. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere between the person drinking mirinda and the person who's hobby is puzzles##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Hobby   | collecting | cooking | puzzles | traveling   |
| Beverage   | mirinda    | lemonade      | tea      | 7up |

