.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-13::.
City: liverpool, new-york, venice, hamburg
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, tennis, cycling, rugby
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
2. the person traveling to hamburg is the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person who's sport is cycling is the person traveling to venice##1
4. the person traveling to venice is not the person who's sport is tennis##6
5. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
6. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere between the person who's sport is surfing and the person traveling to venice##7
7. the person traveling to new-york is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cycling##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| City       | hamburg | liverpool | new-york | venice |
| Sport   | surfing   | rugby      | tennis        | cycling  |

