.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-14::.
4 different games are played: billiard, bridge, backgammon, monopoly
City: paris, boston, san-francisco, hannover
1. the person traveling to boston is in an even position##4
2. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere between the person playing monopoly and the person traveling to san-francisco##7
3. the person traveling to hannover is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is in an even position##4
5. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to boston##5
6. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
7. the person playing bridge is the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Game      | billiard   | backgammon | bridge | monopoly   |
| City   | paris | san-francisco   | hannover | boston |

