.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-15::.
House: ranch-style, wooden, cottage, craftsman
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, april, july, november
1. the craftsman house is somewhere between the wooden house and the person who's birthday is in november##7
2. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##5
3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left##1
4. the wooden house is not the person who's birthday is in november##6
5. the ranch-style house is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who's birthday is in july##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| House   | cottage | craftsman     | ranch-style     | wooden |
| Birthday     | november | july | april | may     |

