.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, coffee, iced-tea, sprite
House: victorian, gothic-revival, townhouse, colonial
1. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the townhouse house##1
3. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking water##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere between the person drinking coffee and the victorian house##7
5. the gothic-revival house is somewhere between the townhouse house and the person drinking water##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3     |   4    |
| Beverage           | water | sprite | iced-tea | coffee  |
| House   | victorian     | gothic-revival   | townhouse    | colonial |

