4. the person watching family movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching western movies##5
5. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3
6. the person watching adventure movies is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |  3   |    4     |
