.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, juice, cola
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, amber, blood-red, blue
1. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person who likes black##5
3. the person drinking iced-tea is not the person who likes amber##6
4. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the person who likes amber##5
5. the person who likes blue is somewhere between the person who likes blood-red and the person drinking iced-tea##7
6. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
7. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person who likes amber##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage           | iced-tea | juice  | fanta  | cola |
| Color   | black  | blue | amber | blood-red   |

