.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-19::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, billiard, backgammon, scrabble
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, pall-mall, bolivar, chaman
1. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
2. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
3. the pall-mall-smoker is somewhere to the left of the siglo-smoker##5
4. the person playing scrabble is on the far left##1
5. the chaman-smoker is not the person playing backgammon##6
6. the pall-mall-smoker is somewhere between the person playing monopoly and the person playing backgammon##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |     3     |   4    |
| Game   | scrabble | backgammon | billiard      | monopoly |
| Cigar     | chaman  | bolivar  | pall-mall | siglo   |

