.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  writer, architect, engineer, electrician
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, bluemaster, game, havana
1. the engineer is somewhere between the alhambra-smoker and the architect##7
2. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
3. the electrician is on the left of the writer##1
4. the bluemaster-smoker is somewhere to the right of the engineer##5
5. the engineer is on the left or right of the game-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Job         | architect    | engineer | electrician     | writer |
| Cigar   | game | havana  | bluemaster | alhambra |

 